<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201013/f58408b851a549b8b747217bf4cf971f.jpeg" max-width="600"><span class="img-desc" style="font-size: 16px;">行书 173x34cm</span></img></p>
